data.description: This immaculate 1.5 story home is waiting for YOU! Cozy up by the fireplace inside or around the firepit in the gazebo outside. Gorgeous pergo flooring throughout and impeccably clean! Home has a large first floor primary bedroom with TWO walk-in closets and showers, one with a jetted tub for relaxing after a long day. Two of the upstairs bedrooms have HUGE walk-in closets. Bonus room upstairs, currently being used as a 4th bedroom, would make an excellent office space. Upstairs also has a full bath and loft area. Large kitchen and dining area with an island and walk-in pantry are perfect for cooking and family gatherings. Third full bath downstairs too! Two car garage with pull down stairs to tons of attic storage. And we can't forget the outdoor space! Enjoy relaxing on the front porch or in the backyard oasis. Roomy back deck and gazebo are perfect for cookouts and fall nights by the fire. Come see for yourself!
